Nkitanapat tomon

(Ena 
20  .
1  -
17  )


1  Neiturrurru Musa iltung'ana pooki le Israel, nejoki ninche, “Entoning intae Israel nkikoot o kuna kitanapat nairo nanu too nkiyiaa inyi ena olong, niyiolouu intae ning'oring'oro ate pee iasiasa. 
2  Eitobirua apa Olaitoriani Enkai ang olning'o lo sotua o iyiook te Horeb. 
3  Mme apa loo papa eitobirie Olaitoriani Enkai ang ele ning'o lo sotua, kake iyiook, kulo pooki ootii ene ooishu ena olong. 
4  Eirorie intae Olaitoriani nchororo nkomomi to ldoinyo, te mpolos eina kima, 
5  ina kata aitashe nanu te rishata Olaitoriani o intae teina kata, pee eibalakinye intae ororei lo Laitoriani; amu itureishote apa te nkaraki ina kima, neitu ilepilepe aapuo enchumata oldoinyo. Nejo ninye:


6  “ ‘Ara nanu Olaitoriani Enkai ino, ilo likiyaua iyie aitupuku te nkop e Misiri, aitupuku te nkaji e sinkaisho.


7  “ ‘Miata kulie aitin neme nanu.


8   “ ‘Mintobiraki kewan enkitanyaanyukoto e nkai nagueta, aashu empukunoto e ae toki natii shumata aashu enatii abori enkop, aashu ina natii atua enkare tiabori enkop; 
9   mirrugokino ninche nimiserem ninche; amu ore nanu Olaitoriani Enkai ino naa kara Enkai olom, naitusuj nkera ing'ok oo loo menye o metabaiki eishoi e uni o eniong'uan e lelo laaiba nanu, 
10  kake kaitodolu enyorrata too nkalifuni e lelo laanyor neibung nkitanapat aainei.


11   “ ‘Mimpot enkarna o Laitoriani Enkai ino te nkiguran: amu meikenaa Olaitoriani ajo eitu eitarruoo ilo oipot enkarna enye te nkiguran.


12   “ ‘Mbung'a enkolong e Sabato, pee intisiny, anaa enikintanapa Olaitoriani Enkai ino. 
13   Too nkolong'i ile taasisho, nias esiai ino pooki; 
14  kake ore enkolong e naapishana naa sabato to Laitoriani Enkai ino; ore teina olong mias hoo ae siai, iyie aashu olayioni lino, aashu entito ino, aashu olaisiaayiani lino, aashu enkaisiaayiani ino, aashu olkiteng lino, aashu osikiria, lino aashu ae ake ninye nabo oo nkishu inono, aashu olomoni otii atua enkaji ino, pee etum aeng'iyeng'ayu olaisiaayiani lino lee o enkaisiaayiani ino tenebo iyie. 
15  Tadamu nchere ira apa osinka te nkop e Misiri, nikintupuku Olaitoriani Enkai ino teine te nkaina enye magilani naitoriori; metaa kintanapa iyie Olaitoriani Enkai ino pee imbung enkolong e Sabato.


16   “ ‘Iyanyita papaai lino o ng'utunyi, anaa enaaitanapa nanu Olaitoriani Enkai ino, pee itum ataseriana, nitum atoponai nkolong'i inono, teina kop naaisho nanu iyie.


17   “ ‘Miar metua


18   “ ‘Miloloito,


19   “ ‘Nimipurrisho.


20   “ ‘Niminteeniki ilo le latia ino elejare.


21   “ ‘Niming'uar enkitok eilo le latia ino; niming'uar enkaji eilo le latia ino, aashu enkurma enye, aashu olaisiaayiani lenye aashu enkaisiaayiani enye, aashu olkiteng lenye, aashu osikiria lenye, aashu pooki toki ake ninye eilo le latia ino.’


22   “Kulo rorei eirorie intae Olaitoriani te umata inyi pooki to ldoinyo eimunye empolos e nkima, o enkatampoi o enaimin kitok, to ltoilo kitok; neitu ninye eitoki aponaa toki. Neiger ninye kulo rorei too soito naagueta, naaisho ninye nanu.

Etureishote iltung'ana

(Ena 
20  .
18  -
21  )


23  “Ore ake pee ining'ining'i ilo toilo epuku te mpolos eina aimin, ina kata eyupuyupito oldoinyo te nkima, nikipuonunu intae aanyikaki, ilukuny pooki oo loshon linyi, olpayiani linyi; 
24  nijojo intae, ‘Ng'ura, eitoduaa iyiook Olaitoriani Enkai ang enkisisa enye o enkitoo, nikitoning'o iyiook oltoilo lenye epuku te mpolos enkima; kitoduaa iyiook ena olong Enkai eirorie iltung'ana neton ake eishu lelo tung'ana. 
25  Amaa naa taata kainyoo iyiook pee kiye? Amu kemut iyiook ena kima kitok; tenikintoki iyiook aaning oltoilo lo Laitoriani Enkai ang, nikiye. 
26  Amu kaing'ae too looishu pooki oata osesen, otoning'o oltoilo le Nkai naishu eiro eimu empolos e nkima, anaa enikitoning'o iyiook, neton ake kinchu. 
27  Enchom entinyikakaki pee ining'ining'i nena pooki naajo Olaitoriani Enkai ang; nilikiki iyiook nena pooki naaliki intae Olaitoriani Enkai ang; amu eikining iyiook nikiaas.’


28  “Nening Olaitoriani irorei linyi ina kata apa pee kirorierie nanu; naajoki nanu Olaitoriani, ‘Atoning'o nanu irorei le kulo tung'ana likitiakitia ninche; eiroro ninche te sipata nena pooki naatejo. 
29  Oi oshi tenaa keeta ena damunoto anaa ena olong nkolong'i pooki, pee aaureyu nanu neibung nkitanapat aainei pooki, pee etum ninche aataseriana tenebo nkera enye ntarasi. 
30  Shomo tiaaki ninche, “Entorrinyokinoto ilng'oborri linyi.” 
31  Kake ore iyie, intasho tene te mbata nanu, pee aaliki nkitanapat pooki, o nkikoot o nkiguanat nilo aiteng'en ninche, pee epuo ninche aas teina kop nalo nanu aisho ninche.’ 
32  Shomo naa toduaa kewan pee ias anaa enikintanapa Olaitoriani Enkai ino; nimimbelekenya alo enkalo e tatene aashu ene kedienye. 
33  Shomo teina oitoi pooki nikintanapa Olaitoriani Enkai ino, pee itum atopuaa, nitum sii ataseriana, nitumutumu aatobikoi tiatua ina kop naisho intae Olaitoriani.

